---
title: Shrimp Gyozas with Edamame Succotash
description: Wonton wrappers make these shrimp gyozas a cinch - just fill, seal, and fry! Juicy shrimp, ginger, and scallion makes for a light and fragrant filling that beats take-out hands down. We've given Southern succotash a Japanese twist for a colorful and healthy side.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54ecd78b6ced6e41738b4567.jpg
